gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bucks 118, 76ers 117
gameRecap.excerpt: Damian Lillard (39 points, eight rebounds, four assists) and Giannis Antetokounmpo (23 points, 13 rebounds) combine for 62 points for the Bucks as they defeat the 76ers, 118-117. Tyrese Maxey (31 points, eight assists) and Kelly Oubre Jr. (27 points) combine for 58 points for the 76ers in the losing effort. The Bucks improve to 1-0 on the season, while the 76ers fall to 0-1.
